0. Basic Definitions.

   "Covered Work" means the Received Work or a Derived Work.

   "Derived Work" means a work of authorship that copies from,
   modifies, adapts, is based on, includes, transforms or translates
   all or part of the Received Work such that copyright permission is
   required. Derived Works do not include Mere Aggregation or the mere
   making of a verbatim copy of the Received Work.

   "Distribute" means to transfer or make available a copy of a work
   to someone else (in the case of an organization, to someone outside
   of the organization), such that copyright permission is required.

   "Distributor" means any individual or organization that
   Distributes a Covered Work, including Us.

   "Mere Aggregation" means an aggregation of a Covered Work with
   another work that is separate from, independent of, and is not by
   its nature an extension or enhancement of, the Covered
   Work. However, if the license of an aggregation restricts users
   from exercising rights under this License with respect to the
   Covered Work, the aggregation is not Mere Aggregation.

   "Received Work" means the particular work of authorship We make
   available to You under this License.

   "We"/"Us"/"Our" refers to the individual or organization that
   places the Received Work under This License.

